fuse: add support for SEEK_HOLE and SEEK_DATA in lseek

A useful performance improvement for accessing virtual machine images
via FUSE mount.

See https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1220173 for a use-case
for glusterFS.

